        "synopsis": {
            "value": "After six years of marriage, 29-year-old Ling Xun Xun files for divorce, finding herself free once again. But her joy is short-lived when she gets into a fender-bender and is saddled with a huge debt. Desperate to regain custody of her son, Xun Xun returns to work as a personal assistant to 23-year-old CEO Cheng Li, only to realize he's the owner of the car she hit. Despite Cheng Li's attempts to\n\ntrouble her, he becomes impressed by Xun Xun's resilience and falls for her. But Xun Xun resists, believing their differences make them incompatible. Will love prevail?",
